headline: Diamondback Energy price target lowered to $174 from $204 at UBS
summary: UBS lowered the firm’s price target on Diamondback Energy (FANG) to $174 from $204 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The firm sees Energy viewed as a recession downside play, the analyst tells investors in a research note. UBS lowered its price target reflecting increased uncertainty around economic activity and commodity prices.
